show.description:
A powerful mutant, Number Seven, vanishes without a trace. A mysterious girl named Vennila reveals she has extraordinary healing powers. And as Number Five lies wounded, chaos begins to unfold.
You, the audience, are thrown into the heart of the storm—where the Queen family must battle not just enemy conspiracies, but the dark world of scientific experiments and political manipulation. Their future teeters on the edge. What do their enemies really want? Can the Queen family survive the mounting pressure? You're about to find out
